Author: Weeb_Trash_420
Text: She blames work on not being able to do anything for me (support wise) yet she makes her own schedule so I call bullshit on that. I didn't know they were related but I feel like I don't have autism (despite being diganosed with it) so that's why I don't want her thinking it comes from that.

Author: slapmyalpaca
Text: I didn’t know what was but I did a quick google search and apparently ARFID is associated with autism spectrum disorder and ADHD, so that might be where that’s coming from.  But if your mum thinks it’s from autism she should really be trying to get you some support for it
